description: If any of you Richmond foodies are feeling famished, then you must come out to Hollywood Cheesesteaks for some deliciousness of glitz & glam proportions. This all-star team is serving up authentic Philly cheesesteaks with savory meats, cheeses, and quality toppings heaped high on scrumptious locally fresh-baked bread. If your diet is vegan or vegetarian, there are plenty of creative and tasty options for you to try too. For flavorful food that deserves the Richmond red carpet treatment, head straight to Hollywood Cheesesteaks!
name: Hollywood Cheesesteaks
